[[File:Cristiano Ronaldo Madrid.jpg|thumb|upright|left|Monga momwe chiwerengero chake chokhalira 7 sichinali kupezeka, Ronaldo ankavala nambala 9 m'nyengo yake yoyamba ku Madrid. Raúl atachoka, Ronaldo anapatsidwa satifiketi 7 patsogolo pake [[2010–11 La Liga|Nyengo ya 2010-11]].]]
Pambuyo pa nyengo ya 2009-10, Ronaldo adagwirizanitsa Real Madrid ndi ndalama zokwana £ 80 miliyoni (€ 94 miliyoni). Msonkhano wake, umene unapitilira mpaka 2015, unali wokwanira € 11 miliyoni pachaka ndipo unali ndi chigamulo chogulitsa € 1 biliyoni. Mafilimu okwana 80,000 adapezeka ku Santiago Bernabéu, kupitirira zaka 25 za mafilimu 75,000 omwe adalandira Diego Maradona ku Napoli. Ronaldo adalandira sheti ya nambala 9, yomwe idaperekedwa kwa iye yemwe anali mtsogoleri wa Madrid, Alfredo Di Stéfano.

Ronaldo adayamba ku [[La Liga]] pa 29 August 2009, motsutsana ndi [[Deportivo de La Coruña|Deportivo La Coruña]], ndipo adapeza malo otsekedwa ku chipinda cha 3-2 cha Madrid.<ref>{{cite news |title=Ronaldo akugonjetsa Real |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8229070.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |date=29 August 2009 |accessdate=29 August 2009}}</ref> Iye adalemba muzitsulo zake zonse zoyambilira ndi klabu, mchenga woyamba wa Madrid kuti achite zimenezo.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/6225577/Cristiano-Ronaldo-makes-Real-Madrid-history.html |title=Cristiano Ronaldo amapanga mbiri ya Real Madrid |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=London |date=23 September 2009 |accessdate=25 August 2010}}</ref>

Zolinga zake zoyamba za Champions League za gululi zinatsatidwa ndi zikhazikitso ziwiri m "gulu loyambalo motsutsana ndi [[FC Zürich|Zürich]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Lachiwiri ndi Champions League |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8257957.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |date=15 September 2009 |accessdate=15 September 2009}}</ref> Chiyambi chake cholimba cha nyengoyi, komabe, anadodometsedwa pamene adamva kuvulala kwa minofu mu Oktoba pamene anali kuntchito padziko lonse, zomwe zinamupangitsa kuti azikhala kwa milungu isanu ndi iwiri.<ref>{{cite news |last=Glendenning |first=Barry |title=Champions League: Milan v Real Madrid – as it happened |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/nov/03/milan-real-madrid-latest-score |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=3 November 2009 |accessdate=22 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Ronaldo forced out of Milan meetings |url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=902721.html |publisher=UEFA |date=11 October 2009 |accessdate=22 April 2014}}</ref> Patatha sabata itabwerera, adalandira khadi lake lofiira loyamba lachifiira ku Spain mumsinkhu wolimbana ndi [[UD Almería|Almería]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Cristiano Ronaldo adatumizidwa ndi chigonjetso chenicheni|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8397610.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |date=5 December 2009 |accessdate=5 December 2009}}</ref> Pakati pa nyengoyi, Ronaldo adaika mzere wachiwiri kwa mpira wa Ballon d'Or ndi mphoto ya FIFA World Player ya Chaka, pambuyo pa [[Lionel Messi]] wa [[FC Barcelona|Barcelona]]], odana nawo a Madrid. Anatsiriza polojekitiyi ndi zolinga 33 mu mpikisano zonse, kuphatikizapo chikhomo cha 4-1 kupambana ndi [[RCD Mallorca|Mallorca]] pa 5 May 2010, yoyamba ku mpikisano wa ku Spain.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2010/may/06/cristiano-ronaldo-real-madrid |title=Cristiano Ronaldo amatsitsa Real Madrid pamsana wa Barcelona|date=6 May 2010 |accessdate=30 August 2014 |work=The Guardian}}</ref> His first season at Real Madrid ended trophyless.<ref>{{cite news |title=Cristiano ronaldo-higuain duo amagwira zolemba zenizeni za madrid|url=http://1x2.eu/top-players/cristiano-ronaldo/the-cristiano-ronaldo-higuain-duo-holds-the-real-madrids-scoring-record/ |work=1x2.eu |date=6 May 2010 |accessdate=6 May 2010}}</ref>

Raúl atachoka, Ronaldo anapatsidwa malaya 7 a Real Madrid patsogolo pake [[2010–11 La Liga|Nyengo ya 2010-11]].<ref name="Raul">{{cite news |url=http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/kits/37525/cristiano-ronaldo-takes-rauls-no-7-shirt-at-real-madrid-benzema-moves-to-no-9-xabi-alonso-takes-no-14.html |title=Cristiano Ronaldo Amagwiritsa Ntchito Chikwama cha Raul ku Real Madrid, Benzema Moves To No.9, Xabi Alonso Akuchita No.14 |accessdate=3 August 2010 |publisher=whoateallthepies.tv |date=3 August 2010}}</ref> Zotsatira zake zinabwerera ku mawonekedwe ake a Ballon d'Or zinagwidwa pamene, kwa nthawi yoyamba mu ntchito yake, Iye adakwaniritsa zolinga zinayi pamsasa umodzi pa 6-1 kupambana ndi [[Racing de Santander|Racing Santander]] pa 23 Oktoba.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/9121629.stm |title=Cristiano Ronaldo adakali anayi ku Real Madrid |date=23 October 2010 |accessdate=30 August 2014 |publisher=BBC}}</ref> Kukweza kwake kunatsiriza masewero asanu ndi atatu otsatizana-atatu ku La Liga, wina ku Champions League, ndipo awiri a Portugal-omwe anali ndi zolinga 11, zomwe adazipeza m'mwezi umodzi. Ronaldo anapezanso zida zotsutsana ndi [[Athletic Bilbao]], [[Levante UD|Levante]], [[Villarreal CF| Villarreal]], ndi [[Málaga CF|Málaga]].<ref>{{cite news |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2010/SPORT/football/11/20/football.real.madrid.barcelona.messi.ronaldo/ |title=Ronaldo akufanana ndi Messi ndipo Real ndi Barca amapita kukapenga |date=20 November 2010 |accessdate=30 August 2014 |publisher=CNN}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/10012011/58/la-liga-ronaldo-hat-trick-sees-real-past-villarreal.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110112193442/http://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/10012011/58/la-liga-ronaldo-hat-trick-sees-real-past-villarreal.html |dead-url=yes |archive-date=12 January 2011 |title=Ronaldo amatsutsa Zakale za Villarreal|date=9 January 2011 |accessdate=30 August 2014 |work=Eurosport |df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Lowe |first=Sid |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2011/mar/04/manuel-pellegrini-malaga-real-madrid |title=No redemption for Manuel Pellegrini on a grim return to the Bernabéu |date=4 March 2011 |accessdate=30 August 2014 |work=The Guardian |location=London}}</ref> Despite his performance, he failed to make the podium for the inaugural [[FIFA Ballon d'Or]] at the end of 2010.<ref>{{cite web |first=Ian |last=Chadband |title=Messi, Ronaldo and Neymar are Ballon d'Or nominees |agency=Reuters |date=30 November 2015 |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-soccer-fifa-ballon-idUKKBN0TJ1LA20151130 |accessdate=29 March 2016}}</ref>


Pamsonkhano wazaka zinayi za '' Clásicos '' otsutsana ndi Barcelona mu April 2011, Ronaldo adalemba kawiri kuti alingane mbiri yake ya 42 pa mpikisano wonse mu nyengo imodzi. Ngakhale kuti analephera kupeza maukonde pamene Madrid adatha kuthetsa masewera a Champions League, adatsutsana ndi malo omwe adzalandire mpikisanowu ndipo adapeza cholinga chogonjetsa maminiti 103 mu [[2011 Copa del Rey Final|Copa del Rey]]. kuwombera koyamba ku Spain.<ref>[http://www.skysports.com/football/match_report/0,19764,11065_3365041,00.html Madrid clinch Copa del Rey] ''[[Sky Sports]]'' Retrieved 20 April 2011 {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110423012003/http://www.skysports.com/football/match_report/0%2C19764%2C11065_3365041%2C00.html |date=23 April 2011 }}</ref> Pa milungu iwiri yotsatira, Ronaldo adajambula zojambula zinayi motsutsana ndi [[Sevilla FC|Sevilla]],<ref>{{cite news |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/SPORT/football/05/07/spain.la.liga.results/ |title=Ronaldo scores 4 as Madrid thrash Sevilla |date=8 May 2011 |accessdate=30 August 2014 |publisher=CNN}}</ref> chipewa chotsutsana ndi [[Getafe CF|Getafe]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/real-madrid-delay-coronation-of-barcelona-as-la-liga-champions-2282286.html |title=Real Madrid delay coronation of Barcelona as La Liga champions |date=11 May 2011 |accessdate=30 August 2014 |work=The Independent}}</ref> ndipo adagonjetsa Villarreal, akutsatira zilembo 38, zomwe zinalembedwa ndi Telmo Zarra ndi Hugo Sánchez.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/competitions/la-liga/8515923/Real-Madrids-Cristiano-Ronaldo-equals-La-Liga-goal-scoring-record-but-hes-not-obsessed-with-scoring-goals.html |title=Cristiano Ronaldo wa Real Madrid akufanana ndi cholinga cha La Liga |date=16 May 2011 |accessdate=30 August 2014 |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=London}}</ref> Zolinga zake ziwiri mu macheza otsiriza a nyengoyi, motsutsana ndi Almería, adamuika kukhala mchenga woyamba ku La Liga kuti apeze masomphenya 40.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13485792 |title=Cristiano Ronaldo amapanga New Primera Liga kukopera nyimbo |date=21 May 2011 |accessdate=30 August 2014 |publisher=BBC}}</ref>

===Juventus===
====2018–19====
Pambuyo pa sabata imodzi yowonongeka, pa July 10, 2018, Ronaldo adasainira mgwirizano wa zaka zinayi ndi chigamulo cha Italiya Juventus atamaliza ndalama zokwana € 100 miliyoni, kuphatikizapo ndalama zothandizana ndi magulu a achinyamata a Ronaldo ndi € 12 miliyoni zina.<ref>{{cite press release |title=Cristiano Ronaldo akuimira Juventus!|url=http://www.juventus.com/en/news/news/2018/cristiano-ronaldo-signs-for-juventus.php |website=juventus.com |date=10 July 2018}}</ref>  Kusamutsidwa kunali kwapamwamba kwambiri kwa wosewera mpira wazaka zoposa 30,<ref>{{cite news |title=Cristiano Ronaldo ku Juventus: Kodi £ 99m atsegula ndalama zabwino kwa akatswiri a ku Italy?|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44785738 |accessdate=10 July 2018 |agency=BBC}}</ref> ndipo wapamwamba kwambiri omwe adalandiridwa ndi chipinda cha Italy. Ronaldo adanena kuti akufunika kuti adziwe ngati akufunika kuchoka pa Real Madrid. Ronaldo adagonjetsa Juventus pamsasa wawo wa Serie A pa 18 August, kupambana kwa Chimwevo 3-2.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.football-italia.net/126430/chievo-thriller-cr7-debut|title=Chievo zokondweretsa pa CR7 poyamba|publisher=Football Italia|date=18 August 2018}}</ref>

